com.vector.annotations.publishedapi

Annotation Type KeepSecretFromPublishedApi


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=CLASS)
 @Target(value={METHOD,CONSTRUCTOR})
 @PublishedApi(value=CLASS_DEPENDENCY)
public @interface KeepSecretFromPublishedApi
    KeepSecretFromPublishedApi hides the marked method or constructor for the PublishedApi, that a Java client is not able to call the marked element.

    A change of an element marked with KeepSecretFromPublishedApi will not lead to a breaking change or any other API change.

    An additional PublishedMethod annotation is not allowed.
